      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先确认一下：ContentCDN 是内容分发节点，ClassroomService 是课堂服务核心，GradeSync 负责成绩同步对吧？另外 LMS Portal 和 StudentDB 也需要纳入吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，LMS Portal 是教师和学生的入口，StudentDB 存储学生数据。ContentCDN 要直接连到 GradeSync，因为成绩页面也需要缓存加速。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出 ContentCDN 到 GradeSync 的连接，同时把 ClassroomService 作为中心节点，分别连向 LMS Portal 和 StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GradeSync 还需要反向连回 StudentDB 获取学生基础信息，同时也要连到 ClassroomService 获取课堂参与数据，这样才能计算综合成绩。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加 GradeSync 到 StudentDB 和 ClassroomService 的双向依赖。现在 StudentDB 和 ClassroomService 都需要连到 GradeSync 作为数据汇聚点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对了，LMS Portal 和 StudentDB 也要直接连到 GradeSync，因为教师从门户提交成绩、学生从数据库验证身份都需要触发同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
